Hot Rock, Andes Power to Explore Geothermal Potential in Andes

-- B y   A l e x   E m e r y
-- 
2011-03-18T20:26:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/hot-rock-andes-power-to-explore-geothermal-potential-in-andes.html
  Hot Rock Ltd. (HRL)  of  Australia  and
Andes Power, a group of investors from  Europe  and the Caribbean,
received authorization to explore  Peru  for geothermal potential,
the Andean nation’s government said.  The two companies will have 24 months to drill in the
southern Andes, Peru’s Energy & Mines Ministry said today in an
e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alexander Emery in Lima at 
 aemery1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
